Package view

Contains specific GUI elements to be contained into the Application

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckInPane
    Purpose of this class is to allow the user to enter the car information and add it to a parking space using the controls displayed.
    CheckOutPane
    Purpose of this class is to allow the user to enter the car information and remove it from its parking space using the controls displayed.
    DeleteUserDialog
    Purpose of this class is to display a ComboBox allowing the user to choosse a username to "delete" from the user data structure.
    GarageMenuBar
    Critical component to the Parking Garage.
    GarageTableView
    GarageTableView is not a table view.
    HistoryPane
    This GUI element displays text that is stored in the project directory, using a date picker to select data created on certain days
    InsertUserPane
    For adding users to the User Data Structure (UserDataManager).
    LoginPane
    Purpose of this class to display the graphical components to allow the user to enter his/her credentials to login to the parking garage program.
    MainMenuPane
    Purpose of this class is that it's a container that contains the GarageMenuBar to enable the user to interact with the Parking Garge.
    MainStage
    Contains the LoginPane where the user is allowed to enter in his/her credentials.
    UserDataViewer
    Purpose of this class is to take a collection of users and display them on a table giving admins the ability to disable or give the selected user admin permissions.
